20:06.560 --> 20:07.599
Vincent?

20:08.640 --> 20:10.399
Vincent!

20:15.960 --> 20:18.279
(QUIET WEEPING)

20:21.920 --> 20:23.679
Vincent, can I help?

20:25.560 --> 20:27.119
It's so clear you cannot help.

20:27.200 --> 20:30.279
And when you leave -
and everyone always leaves -

20:30.360 --> 20:35.399
I will be left once more
with an empty heart and no hope.

20:35.480 --> 20:39.799
DOCTOR: My experience
is that there is, you know,

20:39.880 --> 20:45.439
- surprisingly, always hope.
- Then your experience is incomplete.

20:45.520 --> 20:47.559
I know how it will end.

20:49.120 --> 20:51.359
And it will not end well.

20:58.560 --> 21:00.879
Come on. Come out, let's go outside.

21:00.960 --> 21:02.719
Out!

21:02.800 --> 21:04.999
You get out!

21:05.080 --> 21:08.439
What are you doing here?
What are you doing here?

21:08.520 --> 21:12.959
Very well. I'll leave. I'll leave you.

21:13.040 --> 21:16.839
(VINCENT SOBS)

21:17.080 --> 21:18.919
What's happening?

21:19.000 --> 21:21.119
We're leaving.

21:22.200 --> 21:24.199
Everyone knows he's a delicate man.

21:24.280 --> 21:30.319
