24:48.360 --> 24:50.639
AMY: Quiet.

24:50.720 --> 24:53.799
Is this how time normally passes?

24:53.880 --> 24:57.079
Really slowly.

24:57.160 --> 24:58.799
In the right order.

25:00.280 --> 25:04.719
If there's one thing I can't stand,
it's an unpunctual alien attack.

25:04.800 --> 25:07.359
Are you OK? You seem a bit,

25:07.440 --> 25:09.239
