25:09.320 --> 25:12.639
DOCTOR: There's something not right,
and I can't quite put my finger on it.

25:12.720 --> 25:16.359
There! He's at the window.

25:16.440 --> 25:19.079
- Where?
- There, on the right.

25:19.160 --> 25:21.799
As I thought. Come on.

25:21.880 --> 25:22.839
I'm going in.

25:22.920 --> 25:24.759
- Well, I'm coming too.
- No!

25:24.840 --> 25:28.679
You're Vincent Van Gogh.

25:28.760 --> 25:30.359
No.

25:30.440 --> 25:31.879
But you're not armed.

25:31.960 --> 25:33.399
- I am.
- What with?

25:33.480 --> 25:36.599
Overconfidence, this,
and a small screw driver. I'm sorted.

25:36.680 --> 25:39.719
Just have to find the right
crosactic setting and stun him with it.

25:39.800 --> 25:43.119
Sonic never fails.
Anyway, Amy, only one thought,

25:43.240 --> 25:49.279
