don't follow me under any circumstances.

25:49.360 --> 25:50.919
I won't.

25:55.600 --> 25:58.279
- Will you follow him?
- Of course!

25:59.960 --> 26:01.319
I love you.

26:26.840 --> 26:28.959
(BEEPING)

26:56.000 --> 26:58.479
(LOW GROWLING)

27:21.960 --> 27:25.479
- Has he moved?
- No. Just shifted to the next window.

27:27.040 --> 27:28.479
But wait!

27:28.560 --> 27:30.399
He's turning now.

27:41.760 --> 27:44.039
Damn. He's moved.

27:44.120 --> 27:45.839
(DOCTOR SCREAMS)

27:45.920 --> 27:47.519
- Doctor!
- VINCENT: Amy!

27:53.320 --> 27:55.159
(KRAFAYIS GROWLS)

28:00.360 --> 28:02.279
- Doctor!
- Argh! I thought I told you...

28:02.360 --> 28:05.279
Never mind. We'll talk about it later.
Quick. In here.

28:06.920 --> 28:10.159
(FOOTSTEPS THUD)

28:10.240 --> 28:14.039
DOCTOR (WHISPERING) : Absolutely quiet.

28:14.120 --> 28:17.319
(AMY BREATHES)

28:19.440 --> 28:22.319
Can you breath a little quieter, please?

28:22.400 --> 28:24.759
No!

28:24.840 --> 28:26.279
(KRAFAYIS GROWLS)

28:32.200 --> 28:34.479
