Get back. Get back!

32:22.160 --> 32:23.199
Wah!

32:26.240 --> 32:29.159
- (SQUELCHING)
- Argh!

32:31.080 --> 32:35.479
(WAILING)

32:39.640 --> 32:41.719
He wasn't without mercy at all.

32:41.800 --> 32:43.399
He was without sight.

32:44.960 --> 32:46.479
