of real value to give you.

35:29.040 --> 35:31.599
(DOCTOR GIGGLES)

35:31.680 --> 35:36.919
Oh, no, no. I could never accept
such an extraordinary gift.

35:37.000 --> 35:39.359
Very well.

35:39.440 --> 35:41.439
