than normal people imagine?

36:56.280 --> 36:58.319
Yes.

36:58.400 --> 37:02.279
- Well, brace yourself, Vinny.
- (AMY LAUGHS)

37:30.880 --> 37:32.799
How come I'm the crazy one...

37:32.880 --> 37:35.319
and you two have stayed sane?

